      <title>欧洲央行发现银行商业房地产估值方法存在缺陷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/ecb-finds-weaknesses-in-how-banks-value-commercial-real-estate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区最高金融监管机构警告称，银行在评估数百亿商业房地产贷款的抵押品时存在普遍问题，这凸显出银行可能低估了其受房地产崩盘影响的脆弱性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/ecb-finds-weaknesses-in-how-banks-value-commercial-real-estate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 11:57:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
