    <item>
      <title>热带风暴埃内斯托北上袭击波多黎各</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/tropical-storm-ernesto-drenches-puerto-rico-on-path-northward</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三早上，热带风暴埃内斯托掠过波多黎各，给该岛带来暴雨和强风，约 375,000 户家庭和企业陷入黑暗。风暴很可能在未来几个小时内变成飓风，并向北朝百慕大前进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/tropical-storm-ernesto-drenches-puerto-rico-on-path-northward</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 10:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莱茵金属以 9.5 亿美元国防合同拓展美国业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/rheinmetall-expands-us-footprint-with-950-million-defense-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国莱茵金属公司 (Rheinmetall AG) 计划以 9.5 亿美元收购一家美国军用车辆专家，以扩大其在全球最大国防市场的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/rheinmetall-expands-us-footprint-with-950-million-defense-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 09:18:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油行业并购浪潮逐渐消退，主要公司正在消化交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/oil-patch-m-a-wave-recedes-while-majors-digest-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管石油和天然气行业最大的两家公司埃克森美孚公司和雪佛龙公司在经历了激烈的竞争之后仍在观望，消化各自的大型并购交易，但一些页岩油生产商仍在寻求交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/oil-patch-m-a-wave-recedes-while-majors-digest-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>蒂森克虏伯认为，整个行业增长放缓，需求持续疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thyssenkrupp-s-new-orders-sales-fall-on-broad-industry-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒂森克虏伯股份公司表示，由于该钢铁制造商在汽车技术、机械和建筑领域的客户失去动力，需求疲软导致销售额和新订单下降，这种状况目前仍将持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thyssenkrupp-s-new-orders-sales-fall-on-broad-industry-slowdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 05:07:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
